"2 ounces goat cheese, softened","2 ounces 1/3-less-fat cream cheese, softened","1 tablespoon grated red onion","3/8 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/4 teaspoon garlic powder","8  medium jalapeno peppers, halved vertically and seeded","3  center-cut bacon slices, cooked and crumbled","2 tablespoons red pepper jelly","1 teaspoon water"